<section id="pendaftaran" class="section"><div class="section-heading"><p data-i18n="registration.eyebrow">Tanpa Login</p><h2 data-i18n="registration.title">Pendaftaran Berkas Baru</h2><span data-i18n="registration.desc">Isi data bertahap agar informasi awal tertata sejak pendaftaran.</span></div><div class="wizard"><div class="steps" id="wizardSteps"></div><form id="registrationForm" novalidate enctype="multipart/form-data"><input type="hidden" name="service_key" id="selectedServiceKey"><input type="hidden" name="service_name" id="selectedServiceName"><div class="wizard-panel" data-step="1"><h3 data-i18n="registration.step1">Step 1: Pilih Jenis Transaksi</h3><div class="option-grid" data-options="transactions"></div></div><div class="wizard-panel" data-step="2" hidden><h3 data-i18n="registration.step2">Step 2: Data Pemohon</h3><div class="form-grid"><label><span data-i18n="form.fullName">Nama lengkap</span><input name="fullName" required></label><label><span data-i18n="form.ktp">Nomor KTP</span><input name="ktp" required></label><label><span data-i18n="form.whatsapp">Nomor WhatsApp</span><input name="whatsapp" required placeholder="081234567890"></label><label><span data-i18n="form.email">Email</span><input name="email" type="email" required></label><label class="span-2"><span data-i18n="form.address">Alamat</span><textarea name="address" required></textarea></label><label><span data-i18n="form.actingAs">Bertindak sebagai</span><select name="actingAs" required><option value="" data-i18n="form.choose">Pilih</option><option data-i18n="form.self">Diri sendiri</option><option data-i18n="form.proxy">Kuasa</option><option data-i18n="form.company">Perusahaan</option></select></label></div></div><div class="wizard-panel" data-step="3" hidden><h3 data-i18n="registration.step3">Step 3: Data Pihak</h3><div class="party-grid"><div><label data-i18n="party.first">Pihak pertama</label><div id="firstParties"></div><button type="button" class="text-btn" data-add-party="first" data-i18n="party.addFirst">+ Tambah pihak pertama</button></div><div><label data-i18n="party.second">Pihak kedua</label><div id="secondParties"></div><button type="button" class="text-btn" data-add-party="second" data-i18n="party.addSecond">+ Tambah pihak kedua</button></div></div><div class="toggle-grid"><label><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="proxyFields"> <span data-i18n="party.useProxy">Menggunakan kuasa</span></label><label><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="spouseFields"> <span data-i18n="party.useSpouse">Menggunakan persetujuan suami/istri</span></label><label><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="companyFields"> <span data-i18n="party.useCompany">Menggunakan badan hukum/PT</span></label></div><div class="conditional-fields" id="companyFields" hidden><h4 data-i18n="party.companyData">Data PT</h4><div class="form-grid"><input name="companyName" data-i18n-placeholder="party.companyName" placeholder="Nama PT"><input name="deedNumber" data-i18n-placeholder="party.deedNumber" placeholder="Nomor akta"><input name="skNumber" data-i18n-placeholder="party.skNumber" placeholder="Nomor SK Kemenkumham"><input name="director" data-i18n-placeholder="party.director" placeholder="Direktur"><input name="lastChange" data-i18n-placeholder="party.lastChange" placeholder="Perubahan terakhir"></div></div><div class="conditional-fields" id="proxyFields" hidden><h4 data-i18n="party.proxyData">Data Kuasa</h4><div class="form-grid"><input name="grantor" data-i18n-placeholder="party.grantor" placeholder="Pemberi kuasa"><input name="attorney" data-i18n-placeholder="party.attorney" placeholder="Penerima kuasa"></div></div><div class="conditional-fields" id="spouseFields" hidden><h4 data-i18n="party.spouseData">Data Pasangan</h4><div class="form-grid"><input name="spouseName" data-i18n-placeholder="party.spouseName" placeholder="Nama pasangan"><input name="spouseKtp" data-i18n-placeholder="party.spouseKtp" placeholder="Nomor KTP pasangan"></div></div></div><div class="wizard-panel" data-step="4" hidden><h3 data-i18n="registration.step4">Step 4: Upload Dokumen</h3><p data-i18n="upload.note">Dokumen menyesuaikan jenis transaksi. Format: PDF, JPG, JPEG, PNG. Maksimal 2 MB per file.</p><div id="documentChecklist" class="upload-grid"></div></div><div class="wizard-panel" data-step="5" hidden><h3 data-i18n="registration.step5">Step 5: Konfirmasi</h3><div id="summaryBox" class="summary-box"></div><div class="success-box" id="registrationSuccess" hidden data-i18n="registration.success">Pendaftaran berhasil. Kode tracking Anda adalah TRK-2026-0001. Silakan simpan kode ini untuk mengecek progres berkas.</div></div><div class="form-errors" id="formErrors"></div><div class="wizard-actions"><button type="button" class="secondary-btn" id="prevStep" data-i18n="registration.prev">Sebelumnya</button><button type="button" class="primary-btn" id="nextStep" data-i18n="registration.next">Berikutnya</button><button type="submit" class="primary-btn" id="submitRegistration" hidden data-i18n="registration.submit">Kirim Pendaftaran</button></div></form></div></section>